---
title: Tex-Mex Beyond Meat® Hash with Chipotle Mayo
description: Fancy some breakfast vibes for dinner tonight? Potatoes, hot peppers, corn and tomatoes are roasted to achieve beautiful caramelization before being tossed with Beyond Meat®, onions and spices to create a heavenly hash.
